text: The women's 3000 metres event at the 1978 Commonwealth Games was held on 7 August at the Commonwealth Stadium in Edmonton, Alberta, Canada. It was the first time that this event was held at the Commonwealth Games. ==Results== {| class="wikitable sortable" style=" text-align:center" |- !Rank !! Name !! Nationality !! Time !!
